Revision history for blog.

1.0.1 2014-05-08

  * Properly get assets if in subdirectory
  * Fixed installation instructions

1.0.0 2014-05-07

  * Moved to Flask from Tornado
  * Removed Bootstrap, added Font Awesome
  * Added option for adding custom HTML at the end of the page
  * Added option to change the username and password

0.2.0 2014-04-13

  * Posts are now sorted properly
  * Style/layout improvements
  * Unit tests
  * Link text field does not exist anymore
  * Added option to delete posts

0.1.0 2014-04-08

  * First release
